    <h1>chocolate</h1>
    <hr>
    <p>
        A <strong>chocolate</strong> is a quick and healthy dish.
        It is easy to make and very <em>tasty</em>.
    </p>

    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>milk</li>
        <li>sugar</li>
        <li>dark chocolate</li>
        <li>white chocolate</li>
    </ul>
    <hr>
    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Take cocoa powder, cocoa butter, and sugar.</li>
        <li>Heat cocoa butter on low flame until it melts.</li>
        <li>Add cocoa powder to the melted butter.</li>
        <li>Add sugar and mix well.</li>
        <li>Add vanilla essence for good flavor.</li>
        <li>Mix everything smoothly.</li>
        <li>After it becomes hard, your chocolate is ready! üç´</li>
        <li>Your <strong>chocolate</strong> is ready to eat.</li>
    </ol>
